Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.91,0:04:33.95,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}嗯 有点像我想象的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.91,0:04:35.08,Default-#1,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}马竞内部怎么样？
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.35,0:04:37.82,Default,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}就像一个大家庭
